game.name: Square Run
game.description:
Have you imagined guiding someone on a platform that is full of different kinds of obstacles? Join Square Run and get a pleasure of helping a square shaped character to survive on an endless moving track! This adventure journey is going to be very tough and complicated today as plenty of obstacles in the form of rocket, sharp spikes and more are waiting for it on the track. This brand new adventure game looks pretty challenging to deal with. But, knowing the art of how to avoid obstacles will get you through. 

All it takes to excise to pass and avoid the things that come on your way to survive long on the platform. Do not forget to make a simple jump using a single click or a double jump using a double click to jump over all the dangerous obstacles. One thing is sure that you would have a great fun by controlling a square to run as long as possible. The gameplay of this html5 infinite run game resembles with the Geometry Dash. 

This cool square needs your help urgently. So, try to help it out to run for as long as possible and earn the highest score. Enjoy this cool square running game on various types of devices, including computers, tablets, smartphones, windows phones, android devices, Samsung as well as iPads and iPhones. Give your best to help square avoid all the obstacles and make your new record today! Good luck to try out more endless jumping mobile games for free on atmegame.com, no download required!
